[The synchronous HTTP interface](https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/speech-to-text?topic=speech-to-text-http) provides the simplest way to make a recognition request. You use the POST /v1/recognize method to make a request to the service. You pass the audio and all parameters with the single request. The following curl example shows a basic HTTP recognition request:

